## EthersLiquity.unstakeProtocolToken() method

Withdraw ProtocolToken from staking.

**Signature:**


## Exceptions

Throws [EthersTransactionFailedError](./lib-ethers.etherstransactionfailederror.md) in case of transaction failure. Throws [EthersTransactionCancelledError](./lib-ethers.etherstransactioncancellederror.md) if the transaction is cancelled or replaced.

## Remarks

As a side-effect, the transaction will also pay out the ProtocolToken stake's [collateral gain](./lib-base.protocoltokenstake.collateralgain.md) and [DebtToken gain](./lib-base.protocoltokenstake.debttokengain.md)<!-- -->.
